*SMED MAP: BROWSE_MAP
*DESCRIPTION: Professional browsing interface for Japanese employee data with pagination
*ROWS: 24
*COLS: 80
*CREATED: 2025-07-28
*ENCODING: SJIS/EBCDIC compatible

